title: AudioCodes SBC HA health
agents: snmp
catalog: hw/network/audiocodes
license: GPL
distribution: kuhn-ruess
description:
 Monitors HA keepalive packet loss for active and redundant units. Active HA
 fault, configuration mismatch, switchover and synchronization alarms are
 evaluated from the AudioCodes active alarm table.

inventory:
 One service named {SBC HA Health} is created when HA KPI objects exist.
